%%{init: {"sequence": {"mirrorActors": false}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as Dashboard
    participant API as Backend API
    participant ML as Python ML Server
    participant DB as Database
    
    ML->>ML: Load SetFit Priority Model
    ML->>ML: Load SentenceTransformer (Skills)
    ML->>ML: Load Urgency Logic

    User->>UI: Open Dashboard
    UI->>API: GET /api/tasks/recommendations

    API->>DB: Fetch candidate tasks (To Do / In Progress)
    DB-->>API: List of Tasks
    
    loop For each candidate task
        API->>ML: POST /analyze_task
        ML->>ML: Calculate Priority & Urgency
        ML->>ML: Match Skills (Task vs User Skills)
        ML-->>API: { urgency_score, detected_skills, predicted_priority }
    end

    API->>API: Filter tasks where User is a top match
    API->>API: Sort by Urgency Score

    alt High Urgency Items
        API-->>UI: "Critical Attention Needed" List
    else Standard Queue
        API-->>UI: Ranked Task List
    end

    UI-->>User: Display prioritized recommendations
    
    User->>UI: Accept/Start Task
    UI->>API: Update Status
    API->>DB: Save Change

